'''卡爾·帕金斯'''（{{lang-en|'''Carl Perkins'''}}，1932年4月9日 - 1998年1月19日<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nytimes.com/1998/01/20/arts/carl-perkins-dies-at-65-rockabilly-pioneer-wrote-blue-suede-shoes.html?pagewanted=all |title=Carl Perkins Dies at 65; Rockabilly Pioneer Wrote 'Blue Suede Shoes'，The New York Times，Retrieved 3 November 2014. |accessdate=2014-11-03 |archive-date=2014-11-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141103184235/http://www.nytimes.com/1998/01/20/arts/carl-perkins-dies-at-65-rockabilly-pioneer-wrote-blue-suede-shoes.html?pagewanted=all |dead-url=no }}</ref>）是一位[[美國|美國]]鄉村[[搖滾|搖滾]]音樂人。從1954年開始，在[[田納西州|田納西州]][[孟菲斯_(田納西州)|孟菲斯市]]的太陽唱片錄音室灌錄唱片，他最著名的歌曲是《[[藍色麂皮鞋|藍色麂皮鞋]]》。

==音樂地位==

查理·丹尼爾斯（Charlie Daniels）這樣說：「卡爾·帕金斯的歌曲把[[洛卡比里|鄉村搖滾樂]]的時代擬人化，卡爾·帕金斯的音樂擬人化[[洛卡比里|山區鄉村搖滾]]音樂比任何參與其中的樂手還多，因為他一直堅持到底<ref name="Schor">{{Citation  | last = Naylor  | first = Jerry  | title = They Called It Rockabilly Long Before They Called It Rock and Roll  | place = Milwaukee, US  | publisher = Hal Leonard Corporation  | year = 2007  | edition = 1st  | url = http://books.google.com.tw/books?id=FVx3PQAACAAJ&dq=They+Called+It+Rockabilly+Long+Before+They+Called+It+Rock+and+Roll&hl=zh-TW&sa=X&ei=hZpXVPeuFIbCmAXO2YHQBw&ved=0CB0Q6AEwAA  | isbn = 978-1-4234-2042-2  | accessdate = 2014-11-03  | archive-date = 2014-11-03  | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141103184000/http://books.google.com.tw/books?id=FVx3PQAACAAJ&dq=They+Called+It+Rockabilly+Long+Before+They+Called+It+Rock+and+Roll&hl=zh-TW&sa=X&ei=hZpXVPeuFIbCmAXO2YHQBw&ved=0CB0Q6AEwAA  | dead-url = no  }}</ref>。」帕金斯的歌曲都由知名音樂人（及朋友）灌唱，好有影響力的例如[[埃爾維斯·皮禮士利|埃爾維斯·皮禮士利]]，[[披頭四|披頭四]]樂隊，[[吉米·罕醉克斯|吉米·罕醉克斯]]，和[[尊尼·卡殊|尊尼·卡殊]]，這進一步鞏固了他在流行音樂史的地位。[[保羅·麥卡尼|保羅·麥卡尼]]甚至聲稱：「如果沒有卡爾·帕金斯，就不會有披頭四<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.24-7pressrelease.com/press-release/rock-n-roll-legend-carl-perkins-much-anticipated-story-to-come-to-the-big-screen-32090.php | title = Rock 'n Roll legend Carl Perkins' much anticipated story to come to the big screen | date = 16 August 2007 | accessdate = 3 November 2014 | archive-date = 2014-11-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141103183030/http://www.24-7pressrelease.com/press-release/rock-n-roll-legend-carl-perkins-much-anticipated-story-to-come-to-the-big-screen-32090.php | dead-url = no }}</ref>。」

==榮譽獎項==
被譽為「鄉村搖滾之王」的卡爾·帕金斯，是「[[摇滚名人堂|摇滚名人堂]]」及「[[葛萊美獎|葛萊美名人堂]]」的入選者。2004年，他在《[[滾石雜誌|滾石雜誌]]》的「史上一百個最偉大的藝術家」名單中，排名第九十九位<ref>{{cite journal| title = The Immortals: The First Fifty| issue = 946| journal = Rolling Stone| url = http://www.rollingstone.com/news/story/5939214/the_immortals_the_first_fifty| access-date = 2014-11-03| archive-date = 2010-04-11| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100411041126/http://www.rollingstone.com/news/story/5939214/the_immortals_the_first_fifty| dead-url = yes}}</ref>。

